{"_path":"/resident/r029","_dir":"resident","_draft":false,"_partial":false,"_locale":"","title":"改善通學步道 - 樂善國小","description":null,"image":"/images/resident/r029-01.jpeg","sequence":29,"category":"交通建設","place":"A7重劃區","author":"社區網站","head":{"meta":[{"name":"keywords","content":""},{"name":"robots","content":""},{"name":"author","content":""},{"name":"copyright","content":"© 2025 "},{"name":"og:title","content":"社區網站-地方行政"}]},"publishedAt":"2025-01-13T00:00:00.000Z","toc":true,"body":{"type":"root","children":[{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"改善通學步道-樂善國小"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"改善通學步道 - 樂善國小"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h3","props":{"id":"桃園市通學步道改善規劃"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"桃園市通學步道改善規劃"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/life/breakingnews/4255391"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"自由時報 2023/03/29:"}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n為建構以人為本的友善校園環境，桃園市府推動"},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://oram.tycg.gov.tw/cp.aspx?n=9225"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"通學步道改善計畫"}]},{"type":"text","value":"。 希望在 2、3 年內編列足夠預算，藉由跨局處通力合作機制，逐步改善學童通學環境。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"改善通學步道六項手段分別為；1、建立實體人行道，區隔人流與車流動線，2、增設避車彎及家長接送專區等設置規劃；3、設置無障礙路緣斜坡道，導盲磚，創造行人無礙環境；4、移除影響通行障礙物，增加人行動線淨寬；5、擴大路口停等空間，搭配庇護島及路口島頭、行穿線退縮、檢討號誌時制等方式提升行人停等安全；6、針對周邊巷弄過窄學校，實施時段性禁止進入。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"img","props":{"alt":"r029-70.jpeg","src":"/images/resident/r029-70.jpeg"},"children":[]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"2024 年龜山議員們也積極協助 A7 重劃區的通學步道規劃, 包含"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://www.facebook.com/share/p/1AihkANwkZ/"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"陳雅倫議員 2024/04/16:"}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n樂善國小前方有一塊私人地，雅倫感謝里長、校長及地主的協助，讓樂善國小前方可以做完整的通學步道以及規劃接送區避車彎。 同時雅倫要求通往文德非營利幼兒園的通學步道改善同步實施。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"img","props":{"alt":"r029-61.jpeg","src":"/images/resident/r029-61.jpeg"},"children":[]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://www.facebook.com/share/p/15ZuQN9jgh/"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"李宗豪議員 2023/05/11:"}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n提議學校旁一塊都市計畫的綠地，請龜山區公所評估施作人行道的可行性，希望串連完整通學步道，並充分利用公有土地，讓小朋友上下學更安全"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"img","props":{"alt":"r029-62.jpeg","src":"/images/resident/r029-62.jpeg"},"children":[]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h3","props":{"id":"樂善國小-通學步道改善成果"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"樂善國小 通學步道改善成果"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"在樂善國小前已經"},{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"擴大停等空間"}]},{"type":"text","value":", 包含接送專車的停等專用道設立, 以及有等車遮雨棚設施。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"改善前\n"},{"type":"element","tag":"img","props":{"alt":"r029-71.jpeg","src":"/images/resident/r029-71.jpeg"},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\n改善後\n"},{"type":"element","tag":"img","props":{"alt":"r029-72.jpeg","src":"/images/resident/r029-72.jpeg"},"children":[]},{"type":"element","tag":"img","props":{"alt":"r029-73.jpeg","src":"/images/resident/r029-73.jpeg"},"children":[]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"在"},{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"增加人行動線淨寬"}]},{"type":"text","value":"方面, 原本寬度 1 米，市府規劃預計會拓寬至 1.9 米，改善長度約 550 公尺。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"改善前\n"},{"type":"element","tag":"img","props":{"alt":"r029-74.jpeg","src":"/images/resident/r029-74.jpeg"},"children":[]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"t